message.content: cs.LO, cs.LO is the most likely category as the paper deals with logic and formal verification. Other likely categories include cs.PL (Programming Languages) as the paper deals with action labels and binding names, cs.LF (Logic in Computer Science) as the paper introduces a new logic for transition systems, cs.SE (Software Engineering) as the paper deals with formal verification, and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the paper deals with the structure of transition systems.
